title: Acer Aspire 9300 / 7000 Service Manual Incl. Disassembly
description:
Since im probberly not the only one looking for this guide/manaul i put it here on TPB :)
Used it for changing the TouchPad in my Aspire 9300, and this manual is sure helpfull since i had to take the entire laptop apart just to get to it. :)

Filename: S.G_AS9300_7000_TM7510_BOOK.pdf

Guide and illustrations are for :

Acer
 Aspire 9300 / 7000
 TravelMate 7510


140 pages total



List of chapter topics:

Chapter1 System Specification 
Chapter2 System Utilities 
Chapter3 Machine Disassembly and Replacement 
Chapter4 Troubleshooting 
Chapter5 Jumper and Connector Location 
Chapter6 FRU (Field Replaceable Unit) List



And for the spareparts i used http://www.zandparts.com/acer/index.php
